
Day 11

         Single If : for condition
         if (condition){
         Statement A
         }

         If & Else : Where there are two Option / possibilities

         if (condition){
         Statement A;
         Statement B;
         }else{
         Statement C;}
         Statement D;
         }

         Statement A, B : if condition is TRUE
         Statement C, D : if condition is FALSE


         Multi Branch If : when there are three or more options

          if (condition 1){
          Statement A;
          Statement B;
          }else if{ condition 2){
          Statement C;}
          Statement D;
          } else {
          Statement E;
          Statement F;
          }

          Statement A, B : if condition 1 is TRUE
          Statement C, D : if condition 2 is TRUE and condition 1 is FALSE
          Statement E, F : if condition 1 and 2 are FALSE

          only one block gets executed. -Sadece bir blok çaıştırılır.



